    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's really not that bad tho, i'm not feeling \"emergency\" levels of pain. i've heard people with kidney issues take stuff like tylenol instead, right? is that actually safe to take or is there a specific dose i should stick to so i don't mess anything up? i just want to sleep this off.",
